comments: Adebayo (MIA) is imminently exiting the lane within three seconds.
Durant (BKN) and Strus (MIA) come together and meet at the same point on the perimeter and the contact is marginal.
Durant (BKN) legally contests Vincent's (MIA) jump shot attempt.  Any "high-five" contact after the release is considered incidental.
Adebayo (MIA) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Brown (BKN) and the contact is marginal.
Adebayo (MIA) makes marginal contact with Brown (BKN) pror to the lob pass that does not affect his ability to defend the pass.
Dragic (BKN) maintains a legal guarding position during the post shot attempt by Adebayo (MIA).
Martin (MIA) legally contests Durant's (BKN) jump shot attempt.
Brown (BKN) is the last player to touch the ball before it goes out of bounds.
Dragic (BKN) and Strus (MIA) engage in incidental contact while pursuing the loose ball.
Mills (BKN) commits a take foul on Herro (MIA).
